description:
There are a lot of absurd things in American Horror Story that don’t make sense. We’ll be looking at the most inconsistent and incoherent plot points from America Horror Story. Man, this show is wacky! WatchMojo ranks the most absurd things in AHS. What do you think is the most ridiculous part of AHS? Let us know in the comments!
